04:10.930 --> 04:12.120
CARLTON: Freeloader.
PHIL: Undependable.

04:12.300 --> 04:14.860
ASHLEY: He's not a freeloader.
CARLTON: Lazy. Of course he's lazy.

04:15.030 --> 04:17.970
He works for me.
He's a freeloading, lazy bum.

04:18.130 --> 04:20.600
ASHLEY: Oh, come on.
CARLTON: Believe me, he's lazy.

04:20.769 --> 04:22.170
WILL:
Excuse me. Excuse me.

04:22.340 --> 04:24.000
PHIL: What?
- I said one word.

04:24.270 --> 04:28.340
Come on, y'all.
Like suave, debonair, strong.

04:28.510 --> 04:30.340
What's this for, Will?

04:30.510 --> 04:35.970
Well, you know, the other night,
Lisa said I was kind of, you know, goofy.

04:36.150 --> 04:37.240
ALL:
Yes, that's it.

04:37.420 --> 04:38.890
CARLTON:
Exactly.

04:39.590 --> 04:42.290
We're going to go with goofy, Will.

04:51.970 --> 04:53.300
How you doing, goofy?

04:53.470 --> 04:54.840
[LAUGHING]

04:56.440 --> 04:57.500
Shut up, Carlton.

04:57.670 --> 05:01.040
Well, look, I don't know.
Maybe Lisa tried to give you a hint.

05:01.210 --> 05:04.240
