Next thing you know, she's not calling you.

05:04.980 --> 05:07.540
Yeah, right. You think?

05:07.920 --> 05:11.580
Will, if there's one thing I know,
it's about women not calling.

05:14.190 --> 05:15.850
- Hey. What's up, baby?
- Hey.

05:16.030 --> 05:19.480
- Hey, listen. I'm off in 15 minutes.
- Oh, Will, I'm so excited.

05:19.660 --> 05:22.500
