- Oh, just forget it.

05:41.720 --> 05:43.310
Ooh. I cannot wait to read this.

05:43.490 --> 05:47.220
The last article he wrote, ooh,
it gave me goose bumps.

05:47.390 --> 05:51.050
I'm gonna climb into a hot bubble bath
and get started on this right now.

05:51.230 --> 05:53.020
See you later.

05:55.070 --> 05:56.460
A bubble bath?

05:56.630 --> 05:59.230
"Marvin, take me away. "

06:00.270 --> 06:02.970
I'm saying, how hard could it be
to write a dumb article?

06:03.140 --> 06:04.830
I could write a whole book.

06:05.380 --> 06:06.400
What kind of book?

06:07.110 --> 06:08.700
A good one.

06:08.880 --> 06:13.440
One that real people would wanna read.
You know, with pictures and stuff.

06:13.880 --> 06:16.320
Oh, a coloring book.

06:17.220 --> 06:20.450
No, I'm being serious, Carlton.
How hard could it be to write good?

06:20.620 --> 06:22.650
