06:30.830 --> 06:32.300
WILL:
Oh, sorry.

06:34.000 --> 06:36.440
- Hey, Carlton, thanks for coming along.
- No problem.

06:36.610 --> 06:39.040
The sooner you make money,
you're out of the house...

06:39.210 --> 06:41.470
...and ultimately out of my life.

06:41.780 --> 06:44.250
Hey, man, what do you think
of this title for my book?

06:44.410 --> 06:48.680
<i>I'm gonna call it
Celebrities' Houses At Night.</i>

06:49.290 --> 06:50.810
I may have misjudged you, Will.

06:50.990 --> 06:53.510
