for this girl.

06:53.690 --> 06:56.280
Look at you. Your hair's neat,
your nails are trimmed.

06:56.460 --> 06:58.480
You started flossing again.

06:58.660 --> 07:00.560
Hey, man, look,
I even trim my nose hair.

07:00.730 --> 07:02.100
Check it out.

07:02.900 --> 07:05.870
- Nice job.
- Thanks.

07:06.140 --> 07:08.430
I don't know. It's just wild, man.

07:08.610 --> 07:13.300
You know, it's like Lisa's the first thought
in my mind when I wake up in the morning.

07:13.480 --> 07:15.910
The last thought before I go to sleep.

07:16.080 --> 07:18.550
Man, you know,
I can talk to her about anything.

07:19.750 --> 07:23.780
You know, it's like her face
has just been engraved inside my head.

07:23.950 --> 07:27.320
It's like, say I'm having a bad day.
No matter what it is, just terrible.

07:27.490 --> 07:31.690
It's like, that first second
that I see her beautiful face...

07:31.860 --> 07:34.460
...and she puts her arms around me...

07:34.630 --> 07:36.660
