07:51.050 --> 07:52.070
Carlton!

07:52.250 --> 07:54.770
[TIRES SCREECHING & HORN HONKING]

07:55.690 --> 07:58.620
- Carlton, what is wrong with you, man?
- I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

07:58.790 --> 08:01.520
