this picture doesn't really do it for me.

08:47.070 --> 08:49.940
- I mean, look at it, it's too dark.
- Oh, see, you're not open.

08:50.110 --> 08:54.510
<i>You're not open, man. I'm telling you.
It's Celebrities' Houses At Night.</i>

