09:04.990 --> 09:06.420
Listen. Look at this.

09:06.590 --> 09:07.950
It's not just pictures.

09:08.120 --> 09:10.680
I wrote little stories with them too. Bam!

09:10.930 --> 09:13.330
You didn't notice that one.
See, it's different now.

09:13.500 --> 09:17.060
See, because I'm not just a photographer.
I'm a photographer and a writer.

09:17.230 --> 09:18.760
I'm ambidextrous.

09:18.940 --> 09:20.160
Nice try, huh?

09:20.340 --> 09:21.930
Maybe next time.

09:22.110 --> 09:24.010
Well, fine.

09:24.410 --> 09:25.900
Maybe I am goofy.

09:26.080 --> 09:28.200
Hey, don't forget your pictures here.

09:28.380 --> 09:30.070
Wait. Wait. Wait a minute.

09:30.250 --> 09:34.210
- Is this one Jay Leno?
- Yeah, that's him.

09:34.550 --> 09:36.450
What is he doing here?

09:36.620 --> 09:39.050
