10:00.110 --> 10:02.080
Sign it when you're ready.

10:02.980 --> 10:04.070
WILL:
Ooh.

10:04.350 --> 10:06.980
Ooh, ooh, ooh. Mm-hm. Mm-hm.

10:07.150 --> 10:09.210
Hey, looks good to me, man.

10:13.390 --> 10:15.080
Will?

10:17.030 --> 10:18.930
Will?

10:23.430 --> 10:26.370
<i>WILL [ON SPEAKERS]: Good evening,
you fine Nubian princess.</i>

10:26.540 --> 10:31.530
<i>I set up a little surprise for you tonight,
so just follow instructions and enjoy.</i>

10:31.710 --> 10:32.940
<i>Number one:</i>

10:33.110 --> 10:35.170
<i>Clap twice.</i>

10:38.380 --> 10:40.940
