10:55.230 --> 10:56.720
<i>Number three:</i>

10:56.900 --> 11:00.960
<i>Take your sexy little self
on over to the couch and have a seat.</i>

11:04.170 --> 11:06.040
<i>Number four:</i>

11:06.510 --> 11:08.200
<i>Get naked.</i>

11:09.480 --> 11:10.500
What?

11:10.680 --> 11:13.440
<i>WILL: No, my fault. I was just kidding.
I was just kidding.</i>

11:13.620 --> 11:15.240
<i>All right. Number five:</i>

11:15.420 --> 11:17.150
<i>Turn around.</i>

11:27.230 --> 11:31.130
Ooh. You sure do know
how to make a girl feel special.

11:31.300 --> 11:33.290
Will, what is all of this about?

11:33.470 --> 11:35.700
