11:41.510 --> 11:44.340
Hey, look.
I wanna give you some goose bumps too.

11:44.510 --> 11:46.540
Mm. Okay, so where's the article?

11:46.720 --> 11:48.840
- Let me see it.
- Eh, eh, eh. In due time.

11:49.020 --> 11:52.580
- In due time. It's all a surprise, baby.
