11:54.420 --> 11:55.690
LISA:
Hoo.

11:55.990 --> 11:58.050
[WILL CLEARS THROAT]

12:00.430 --> 12:01.990
Lisa.

12:02.170 --> 12:04.930
Sweetheart,
there's only one word to describe you.

12:05.100 --> 12:07.000
Scum.

12:07.640 --> 12:08.700
WILL:
Carlton.

12:09.710 --> 12:10.970
Man, you know the routine.

12:11.140 --> 12:14.440
When there's a sock in the door,
you sleep on the lawn.

12:15.980 --> 12:18.170
<i>Have you read
this week's National Inquisitor?</i>

12:18.350 --> 12:19.750
Man, I don't read that trash.

12:19.920 --> 12:21.710
Then how come you're writing it?

12:27.660 --> 12:30.020
Wait, wait.
Whoa, whoa, whoa, wait a minute.

12:30.190 --> 12:33.590
They used one of my photos from my book
and put it in here.

12:33.760 --> 12:38.460
"'Jay Leno: Earth Enemy Number One'
by Will Smith?"

12:38.630 --> 12:41.430
You sold pictures
to a sleazy magazine like this?

12:41.600 --> 12:43.770
No, no, no, baby. I did not.

12:43.940 --> 12:45.570
