12:45.740 --> 12:49.180
Look, Jay Leno wasn't holding an oil can.
He was holding a coffee pot.

12:49.350 --> 12:51.470
That guy tricked me.

12:52.080 --> 12:53.280
Well, at least I got paid.

12:56.720 --> 12:59.550
- Master William, you have a visitor.
- Will Smith?

13:00.190 --> 13:02.950
- Yes, sir.
- You're served.

13:08.500 --> 13:11.260
