to clean up this mess, huh?

13:48.840 --> 13:50.430
Well, yeah. You know the routine.

13:50.610 --> 13:52.800
I do something stupid,
you clean it all up.

13:52.980 --> 13:55.440
The only difference is this time,
I didn't do nothing.

13:55.610 --> 13:58.310
I think you've taken troublemaking
to a whole new plateau.

13:58.480 --> 14:01.470
Wait a minute. Come on.
You gotta know somebody down there.

14:01.650 --> 14:03.080
A cameraman, a makeup girl.

14:03.250 --> 14:06.550
Maybe you sentenced one of the guys
in the band or something.

14:06.720 --> 14:11.320
Will, there is a bigger issue involved here.
I can't keep pulling your butt out of the fire.

14:11.490 --> 14:13.390
You're right. You're right, Uncle Phil.

14:13.560 --> 14:18.870
Look... And this is the last two
or few times. I promise.

14:19.900 --> 14:21.670
You know, Will, there comes a time...

14:21.840 --> 14:25.240
Oh, not the "there comes a time" speech.

14:25.410 --> 14:27.770
I'd pay $10 million
to not have to hear that again.

14:27.940 --> 14:30.380
I'd pay $10 million
so I didn't have to say it again.

14:30.550 --> 14:33.040
Fine. If you don't wanna help me,
just say that.

14:33.220 --> 14:35.550
I got myself into this mess,
I'll get myself out.

14:35.720 --> 14:37.080
I don't need nobody.

14:43.090 --> 14:46.760
Why don't I watch you handle this one,
I'll get the next one, all right?

14:54.100 --> 14:57.830
I can't believe that that realtor
wasted my time on that dump.

14:58.010 --> 15:01.000
Hilary, that house was gorgeous.
What's the problem?

15:01.180 --> 15:04.170
Problem? Well, for starters, the layout.

15:04.510 --> 15:08.510
Say I'm having a small garden party
for 50 of my closest friends...

15:08.680 --> 15:11.410
...and someone spills cocktail sauce
on their Armani suit.

15:11.590 --> 15:15.250
