through the gazebo into the living room...

15:15.420 --> 15:18.590
...past the library and up the steps
to get to the laundry room.

15:20.130 --> 15:21.820
Hilary, that's ridiculous.

15:22.470 --> 15:25.660
You're right.
Who cares how far Hildegard has to walk?

15:30.140 --> 15:31.770
Is there anything I can do to help?

15:31.940 --> 15:34.240
Can you drive a getaway car?

15:34.410 --> 15:36.210
Master William, come quickly.

15:38.950 --> 15:41.610
<i>- They're talking about you on the telly.
PEOPLE [ON TV]: Save our sewers.</i>

15:41.780 --> 15:46.020
<i>- Save our sewers. Save our sewers.
- This is Andrea White of KFPB.</i>

15:46.190 --> 15:48.450
<i>It has been reported
to the National Inquisitor...</i>

15:48.620 --> 15:51.460
<i>...that Tonight Show host Jay Leno
is a toxic polluter.</i>

15:51.630 --> 15:53.030
<i>Will Smith is the young man...</i>

15:53.200 --> 15:56.100
<i>...who photographed Leno dumping oil
into the sewer systems.</i>

15:56.270 --> 16:00.730
<i>His story also alleges that Mr. Leno
may be single-handedly responsible...</i>

16:00.900 --> 16:03.630
<i>...for destroying the rain forest,
the ozone layer...</i>

16:03.810 --> 16:07.040
<i>...and the one tree
that grows in Brooklyn.</i>

16:08.840 --> 16:10.780
Oh, that poor little tree.

16:11.250 --> 16:14.580
Forget that tree, Ashley.
Come on, I'm getting railroaded.

16:14.750 --> 16:16.910
Well, I finally contacted Leno's lawyer.

16:17.090 --> 16:20.350
- Yeah? What'd he say?
- Well, I'm sorry, but it doesn't look good.

16:20.520 --> 16:22.050
I'm afraid you're liable.

16:24.360 --> 16:26.330
[CARLTON CHUCKLING]

16:29.030 --> 16:30.560
What is so funny?

16:30.730 --> 16:34.360
