Those are homonyms.

16:35.170 --> 16:38.570
Carlton,
your next crack is gonna be in your head.

16:39.080 --> 16:40.510
Try it and I'll sue.

16:40.680 --> 16:42.580
[LAUGHING]

16:45.450 --> 16:46.880
Well...

16:47.120 --> 16:49.240
...I know what I gotta do.

16:51.920 --> 16:54.650
He's not gonna do anything stupid,
is he?

16:54.820 --> 16:57.450
You don't know him very well, do you?

16:58.860 --> 17:01.920
<i>It's The Tonight Show.
I'm doing the Bill Clinton McDonald's bit.</i>

17:02.100 --> 17:03.330
It's my best joke.

17:03.500 --> 17:06.020
You're my agent.
I'm the one who should be nervous.

17:06.200 --> 17:09.260
I'll call you after the show, okay?
Yeah. Bye.

17:10.569 --> 17:12.400
[MOUTHING]

17:17.109 --> 17:18.740
Hey, bro. How you doing?

17:18.910 --> 17:20.109
Have you seen Jay Leno?

17:20.579 --> 17:22.920
